Nora Gordon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nora_Gordon 0 Nora Gordon (29 November 1893, West Hartlepool, County Durham – 11 May 1970, London) was a British film and television actress. She was married to Leonard Sharp. Her daughter is the actress Dorothy Gordon.
